lyrics:
[Verse]
I step on the court, feel it in my soul
Dribbling and shooting, I'm in control
Crossing opponents, leaving them in awe
I'm the MVP, they all know the score

[Chorus]
Ballin' on the court, we never back down
Shootin' for the stars, we wear the crown
Ain't no stopping us, we breakin' through
In this game of hoops, we always stay true
